{"tid":644532,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"小學老師入","createTime":"2018-04-27T10:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T11:21:32.000Z","uid":125279,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3502107ca22c7f5f7bc44ed1e9d1125791038066","tid":644532,"uid":125279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"話說最近接左份part time, 係負責教一班低年班嘅小朋友，咁我之前都有做過下私補，諗住都應付到，點佢地真係曳得好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下下都得寸進尺，想惡先肯聽話，想對佢地好啲都唔得，唔怪得當年啲小學老師全部都有燥狂症咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲自問好叻教小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，到底除左鏟到佢地上天之外，仲有啲咩方法先可以令班o靚仔o靚妹聽聽話話？"},{"pid":"d957015fdc91575f6ae59ec436fe9dc3b26e71a9","tid":644532,"uid":93395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"用獎勵 奬下貼紙<br />\n<br />\n送下糖仔<br />\n<br />\n利申 做過功課輔導 想一巴巴煎死班好嘈既細路"},{"pid":"8aa25a27933750344f24b22d2b6ac86bb4353195","tid":644532,"uid":34259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:08:26.000Z","msg":"拍下手，叫佢地做下動作"},{"pid":"c764e4402a624e73c825b6117883073074f81b3e","tid":644532,"uid":125279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d957015fdc91575f6ae59ec436fe9dc3b26e71a9","tid":644532,"uid":93395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"用獎勵 奬下貼紙<br />\n<br />\n送下糖仔<br />\n<br />\n利申 做過功課輔導 想一巴巴煎死班好嘈既細路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:16:38.000Z","msg":"無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地拎完就會打回原形，有時覺得係因為佢地上完成日堂，根本好難再高度集中，但啲老師又成日巡房，想比佢地玩下都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都想一巴煎落去佢地到，有啲人仔細細就已經串過馬撚，又無禮貌又多事，真係唔該唔識教咪鬼生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c24e825f86c682d318aef2748abd02726fc693","tid":644532,"uid":125279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa25a27933750344f24b22d2b6ac86bb4353195